== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
1997年，製片人[[大衛·海曼|大衛·海曼]]正在尋找一本兒童讀物可編成一部廣受歡迎的電影，他曾計劃製作[[黛安娜·韋恩·瓊斯|黛安娜·韋恩·瓊斯]]的小說《{{link-en|食人魔樓下|The Ogre Downstairs}}》，但他的計劃最後告吹了。他在[[盛日影业|盛日影业]]的工作人員後來提出《[[哈利波特－神秘的魔法石|哈利波特－神秘的魔法石]]》的建議，他的助手相信這是個「好主意」。海曼把這想法交給[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]，並在隨後那年[[J·K·羅琳|J·K·羅琳]]將首四部《哈利波特》小說的版權出售，據報約$1,982,900美元<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.quick-quote-quill.org/articles/2000/0700-austfinrev-bagwell.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060908060751/http://www.quick-quote-quill.org/articles/2000/0700-austfinrev-bagwell.html |archivedate=2006-09-08 |work=Australian Financial Review |title=WiGBPd about Harry |date=2000-07-19 |accessdate=2007-05-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。羅琳對製作嚴格要求主要劇組人員必須要[[英國|英國]]人，儘管如此她也容許加入[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]演員，如飾演[[鄧不利多|鄧不利多]]的[[李察·哈里斯|李察·哈里斯]]，因為小說中的人物也設定如此<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2001/nov/16/jkjoannekathleenrowling |archivedate=2013-09-30 |work=[[衛報|The Guardian]] |title=Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone |date=2001-11-16 |accessdate=2016-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130930184717/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2001/nov/16/jkjoannekathleenrowling |dead-url=no }}</ref>。羅琳對出售版權感到猶豫，因為「她不想通過出售人物的版權，讓別人控制故事的其餘部分」，使華納兄弟公司製作並非由作者撰寫的續集<ref>{{cite video |people=Ross, Jonathan, [[J·K·罗琳|J. K. Rowling]] |date=2007-07-06 |title=Friday Night with Jonathan Ross |publisher=BBC One |url=http://www.accio-quote.org/articles/2007/0706-bbc-ross.html |accessdate=2007-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070816113549/http://www.accio-quote.org/articles/2007/0706-bbc-ross.html |archive-date=2007-08-16 |dead-url=no }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.accio-quote.org/articles/2007/0706-bbc-ross.html |date=20200416171911 }}</ref>。

儘管[[史蒂芬·史匹柏|史蒂芬·史匹柏]]最初商談為電影執導，但他拒絕了這個提議<ref>{{cite news |url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/034/034089p1.html |title=No "Harry Potter" for Spielberg |accessdate=2007-07-08 |date=2000-02-23 |publisher=IGN |first=Brian |last=Linder |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071123181415/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/034/034089p1.html |archivedate=2007-11-23 }}</ref>，據報導史匹堡想改編成一個[[動畫電影|動畫電影]]，由美國演員[[哈利·喬·奧斯蒙|哈利·喬·奧斯蒙]]聲演哈利波特<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,275704_2,00.html |title=Potter's Field |date=2000-03-17 |accessdate=2007-05-26 |first=Jeff |last=Jensen |work=Entertainment Weekly |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070331144629/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,275704_2,00.html |archive-date=2007-03-31 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，或在小說續集的元素納入個電影中<ref name="ew" />。史匹柏說，在他的角度就好似「甕中捉鱉，就像[[灌籃|灌籃]]一樣。比方說收回十億美元，並把它變成你的個人銀行帳戶，沒有挑戰性。」<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywood.com/news/detail/id/1091358 |publisher=Hollywood.com |title=For Spielberg, Making a Harry Potter Movie Would Have Been No Challenge |date=2001-09-05 |accessdate=2007-05-26 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120629112720/http://www.hollywood.com/news/Quote_of_the_Day_Spielberg_on_not_making_Harry_Potter/1091358 |archive-date=2012-06-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，史匹柏離開後，開始與其他導演談判，包含：[[克里斯·哥倫布|克里斯·哥倫布]]、[[泰瑞·吉連|泰瑞·吉連]]、[[強納森·德米|強納森·德米]]、[[麥可·紐威爾|麥克·紐威爾]]、[[亞倫·帕克|亞倫·帕克]]、[[沃尔夫冈·彼得森|沃夫岡·彼得森]]、[[羅伯·萊納|羅伯·萊納]]、[[伊萬·雷特曼|伊萬·雷特曼]]、[[提姆·羅賓斯|提姆·羅賓斯]]、{{link-en|布萊德·希伯林|Brad Silberling}}、[[奈·沙馬蘭|奈·沙馬蘭]]以及[[彼得·威爾|彼得·威爾]]<ref name="ew" /><ref name="greg">{{cite web |url=http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/preview/1808404331 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071215132239/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/preview/1808404331 |archivedate=2007-12-15 |title=Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone (2001) |accessdate=2008-08-09 |first=Greg Dean |last=Schmitz |publisher=Yahoo! |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=15294 |title=A Good Night for Harry Potter? |author=Douglas, Edward |accessdate=2007-10-20 |date=2006-07-10 |publisher=ComingSoon.net |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011115845/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=15294 |archive-date=2007-10-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。彼得森和萊納而後都在2000年3月退出了甄選<ref>{{cite news |url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/034/034092p1.html |title=Two Potential "Harry Potter" Director's Back Out |accessdate=2007-07-08 |date=2000-03-07 |first=Brian |last=Linder |publisher=IGN |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080302173529/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/034/034092p1.html |archivedate=2008-03-02 }}</ref>，選擇範圍縮小到了希伯林、哥倫布、帕克與吉連<ref>{{cite news |url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/034/034096p1.html |title=Harry Potter Director Narrowed Down |accessdate=2007-07-08 |date=2000-03-15 |publisher=IGN |first=Paul |last=Davidson |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081206110421/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/034/034096p1.html |archivedate=2008-12-06 }}</ref>。羅琳的第一選擇為泰瑞·吉連<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.wizardnews.com/story.20050829.html |title=Terry Gilliam Bitter about Potter |accessdate=2007-07-08 |date=2005-08-29 |publisher=Wizard News |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070811035807/http://www.wizardnews.com/story.20050829.html |archive-date=2007-08-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但華納兄弟選擇了克里斯·哥倫布，引用他對其他電影的表現，如《[[小鬼當家|小鬼當家]]》、《[[窈窕奶爸|窈窕奶爸]]》等，皆是其決定的關鍵<ref name="columbus">{{cite news |url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/034/034098p1.html |title=Chris Columbus to Direct Harry Potter |accessdate=2007-07-08 |date=2000-03-28 |publisher=IGN |first=Bran |last=Linder |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080113042745/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/034/034098p1.html |archivedate=2008-01-13 }}</ref>。在女儿的劝说下，哥伦布读了前三部作品，结果成了系列的忠实拥趸，打电话给经纪人，要和华纳兄弟开会，商讨导演事宜。听到经纪人说至少有25名导演参与竞标，哥伦布便让他确保自己是最后一个接受会面，好留下“持久的印象”，成为制片方“最先想起的人”。在两个礼拜的等待时间中，哥伦布从导演的角度写了一份130页的剧本，阐述对电影基调的看法。多个华纳高管参与当天的会谈，包括{{tsl|en|Alan Horn|阿兰·霍恩}}。哥伦布热情洋溢地讲了45分钟，展示了写满注释的剧本。过了几个礼拜，制片方通知哥伦布拿下工作，接他去苏格兰见罗琳和海曼<ref>{{Cite web |last=Perez |first=Lexy |date=2000-11-11 |title='Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone' Turns 20: Director Chris Columbus Reflects on Pressures to Adapt Book and Hopes to Direct 'Cursed Child' |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-features/chris-columbus-harry-potter-and-the-sorcerers-stone-20th-anniversary-1235034578/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211111181757/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-features/chris-columbus-harry-potter-and-the-sorcerers-stone-20th-anniversary-1235034578/ |archive-date=2021-11-11 |access-date=2021-11-15 |website=The Hollywood Reporter}}</ref>。他用两个小时阐释自己对电影的看法，打算将麻瓜的戏份打造得“黯淡无光”，同时将魔法世界的场景布置得“充满色彩、情绪和细节”。他参考[[大卫·利恩|大卫·利恩]]改编《[[遠大前程_(1946年電影)|远大前程]]》（1946）及《{{tsl|en|Oliver Twist (1948 film)|雾都孤儿 (1948年电影)|雾都孤儿}}》（1948）的作品，希望用上两部作品的黑暗前卫元素及摄影品质，还参考《[[孤雛淚_(電影)|孤雛淚]]》（1968）及《[[教父_(電影)|教父]]》（1972）的色彩设计<ref name="JensenEW2001p3">{{Cite news |last1=Jensen |first1=Jeff |last2=Fierman |first2=Daniel |date=2001-09-14 |title=Inside Harry Potter |page=3 |work=Entertainment Weekly |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,254808_3,00.html |url-status=dead |access-date=2010-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090203212848/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,254808_3,00.html |archive-date=2009-02-03}}</ref>。

[[史提夫·克羅夫斯|史提夫·克羅夫斯]]获选为影片编剧。他认为改编原著的工作十分艰巨，觉得原作对改编电影及后两部作品的作用不大<ref name="SragowSalon2000">{{Cite web |last=Sragow |first=Michael |date=2000-02-24 |title=A wizard of Hollywood |url=https://www.salon.com/2000/02/24/kloves/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200309083244/https://www.salon.com/2000/02/24/kloves/ |archive-date=2020-03-09 |access-date=2007-07-08 |website=Salon}}</ref>。华纳兄弟经常将要改编成电影的小说的概要发给他，他“几乎没读过”，唯独是《哈利·波特》让他心头为之一振<ref name="JensenEW2001p2">{{Cite news |last1=Jensen |first1=Jeff |last2=Fierman |first2=Daniel |date=2001-09-14 |title=Inside Harry Potter |page=2 |work=Entertainment Weekly |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,254808_2,00.html |url-status=dead |access-date=2010-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081011081939/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,254808_2,00.html |archive-date=2008-10-11}}</ref>。他马上买了这本书，很快便成为系列的拥趸<ref name="SragowSalon2000" />。跟华纳兄弟交涉时，他说影片必须充满英国风，必须忠于原著角色<ref name="SragowSalon2000" />。第一次见罗琳的时候，克罗夫斯紧张不已，希望不让对方觉得自己会毁了她的心血之作<ref name="JensenEW2001p2" />。罗琳说她“本来做好了恨斯蒂夫·克罗夫斯的准备”，但克罗夫斯第一次见她的时候，对她说：“你知道我最喜欢的角色是谁吗？”她想了想，觉得是罗恩，但他说是“赫敏”，感化到她<ref name="JensenEW2001p2" />。罗琳掌握着把关创意的大部分权力，哥伦布不介意<ref name="JensenEW2001p2" />。

华纳兄弟一开始在2001年7月4日上映电影，给制片预留下的窗口期很短，以至于几位有意愿的导演纷纷退出。考虑到时间局限，档期推迟到2001年11月16日<ref name="LinderIGNMay2000">{{Cite web |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2000-05-17 |title=Bewitched Warner Bros. Delays Potter |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/05/17/bewitched-warner-bros-delays-potter |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224091958/https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/05/17/bewitched-warner-bros-delays-potter |archive-date=2015-12-24 |access-date=2020-04-16 |website=IGN}}</ref>。

=== 選角 ===
罗琳坚持采用全英演出阵容<ref>{{Cite news |date=2001-11-16 |title=Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone |work=The Guardian |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2001/nov/16/jkjoannekathleenrowling |url-status=live |access-date=2020-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407105411/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2001/nov/16/jkjoannekathleenrowling |archive-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>。选角导演苏茜·费吉斯（Susie Figgis）与哥伦布和罗琳共同负责哈利、罗恩及赫敏的选角<ref name="LinderIGNMar2000">{{Cite web |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2000-03-30 |title=Chris Columbus Talks Potter |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/03/30/chris-columbus-talks-potter |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104205453/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/03/30/chris-columbus-talks-potter |archive-date=2016-11-04 |access-date=2020-04-16 |website=IGN}}</ref>，演员公开招募<ref>{{Cite web |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2000-05-30 |title=Attention All Muggles! |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/05/30/attention-all-muggles-2 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181115030930/https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/05/30/attention-all-muggles-2 |archive-date=2018-11-15 |access-date=2020-04-16 |website=IGN}}</ref>，但仅限英国儿童<ref name="LinderIGNJul2000-2">{{Cite news |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2000-07-11 |title=Harry Potter Casting Frenzy |work=IGN |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/06/14/harry-potter-casting-frenzy |url-status=live |access-date=2020-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003152308/https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/06/14/harry-potter-casting-frenzy |archive-date=2017-10-03}}</ref>。试镜活动主要分三个环节，参加者朗读完小说的一页内容，即兴表演学生抵达霍格沃兹学院的场景，最后在哥伦布面前朗读几页剧本<ref name="LinderIGNJul2000-2" />。哥伦布为1985年电影《{{tsl|en|Young Sherlock Holmes|少年福尔摩斯}}》创作的剧本也在试镜活动中被采用<ref name="LinderIGNJul2000-3">{{Cite web |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2000-07-11 |title=Trouble Brewing with Potter Casting? |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/07/11/trouble-brewing-with-potter-casting |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208141809/https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/07/11/trouble-brewing-with-potter-casting |archive-date=2019-12-08 |access-date=2020-04-16 |website=IGN}}</ref>。2000年7月11日，费吉斯不满哥伦布忽略数千个有试镜潜质的儿童，愤然离开剧组<ref name="LinderIGNJul2000-3" />。到2000年8月，[[艾倫·瑞克曼|艾倫·瑞克曼]]和[[李察·哈里斯|李察·哈里斯]]分别进入出演西弗勒斯·斯内普和阿不思·邓布利多的最后谈判<ref>{{Cite web |last=Davis |first=Simon |date=2000-08-11 |title=Rickman and Harris lined up for Potter film |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1352305/Rickman-and-Harris-lined-up-for-Potter-film.html |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412191408/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1352305/Rickman-and-Harris-lined-up-for-Potter-film.html |archive-date=2019-04-12 |access-date=2020-07-15 |website=The Daily Telegraph}}</ref>，最终在同月晚些时候确认出演<ref name="SussmanCNN2000p2">{{Cite web |last=Sussman |first=Paul |date=2000-08-23 |title=British child actor 'a splendid Harry Potter' |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2000/WORLD/europe/08/22/potter.casting.02/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191229215056/http://edition.cnn.com/2000/WORLD/europe/08/22/potter.casting.02/ |archive-date=2019-12-29 |access-date=2010-02-07 |work=CNN}}</ref>。2000年8月14日，罗琳的心水人选[[瑪姬·史密芙|瑪姬·史密芙]]和[[羅比·科特瑞恩|羅比·科特瑞恩]]确认出演米奈娃·麦格教授和鲁伯·海格<ref>{{Cite news |last=Davies |first=Hugh |date=2000-08-14 |title=Author's favourites are chosen for Potter film |work=The Daily Telegraph |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1352721/Authors-favourites-are-chosen-for-Potter-film.html |url-status=live |access-date=2017-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329140109/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1352721/Authors-favourites-are-chosen-for-Potter-film.html |archive-date=2020-03-29}}</ref>。2000年8月21日，[[丹尼尔·拉德克利夫|丹尼尔·拉德克利夫]]与新秀演员[[魯伯特·葛林|魯伯特·葛林]]、[[艾玛·沃森|艾玛·沃森]]分别获选为扮演哈利·波特、罗恩·韦斯莱及赫敏·格兰杰的人选<ref>{{Cite web |date=2000-08-21 |title=Daniel Radcliffe, Rupert Grint and Emma Watson Bring Harry, Ron and Hermione to Life for Warner Bros. Pictures "Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone" |url=http://movies.warnerbros.com/pub/movie/releases/harrycast.html |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070404184713/http://movies.warnerbros.com/pub/movie/releases/harrycast.html |archive-date=2007-04-04 |access-date=2007-05-26 |website=Warner Bros.}}</ref>。2000年11月，[[茱莉·華特絲|茱莉·華特絲]]和[[约翰·克里斯|约翰·克里斯]]加盟剧组，分别出演莫莉·韦斯莱和差点没头的尼克<ref>{{Cite web |date=2000-11-07 |title=Walters joins Potter cast |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/1011528.stm |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030134440/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/1011528.stm |archive-date=2019-10-30 |access-date=2020-07-15 |work=BBC News}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=de Graaf |first=Belinda |date=2000-11-13 |title=John Cleese in film over Harry Potter |trans-title=John Cleese in film about Harry Potter |url=https://www.trouw.nl/nieuws/john-cleese-in-film-over-harry-potter~bba3cf0d/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200715032919/https://www.trouw.nl/nieuws/john-cleese-in-film-over-harry-potter~bba3cf0d/ |archive-date=2020-07-15 |access-date=2020-07-15 |website=Trouw |language=nl}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
[[File:Alnwick_Castle_-_Northumberland_-_140804.jpg|thumb]]取景。]]
英国政府电影产业部门的两名官员希望影片能在英国拍摄，提出协助勘景工作，出动[[华纳兄弟利维斯登工作室|利维斯登工作室]]，乃至修改英国童工法，稍微增加每周的工作时间，让在片场工作儿童的工作时间更为灵活<ref name="JensenEW2001p3" />。华纳兄弟接受对方的提议。[[主体拍摄|主体拍摄]]于2000年9月29日在利维斯登工作室启动<ref name="TCMNotes">{{Cite web |title=Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone - Miscellaneous Notes |url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/451961/Harry-Potter-and-the-Sorcerer-s-Stone/misc-notes.html |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181118224211/http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/451961/Harry-Potter-and-the-Sorcerer-s-Stone/misc-notes.html |archive-date=2018-11-18 |access-date=2015-10-21 |website=Turner Classic Movies}}</ref>。[[北约克郡|北约克郡]]{{tsl|en|Goathland railway station|戈斯兰火车站}}的戏份于2000年10月2日开拍。[[坎特伯雷座堂|坎特伯雷座堂]]和苏格兰的因弗莱洛特城堡被奉为霍格沃兹学院的可能取景点，只不过坎特伯雷认为影片展现“异教”主题，拒绝了制片方的请求<ref>{{Cite web |date=2000-06-28 |title=All 7 Harry Potter Books to Film? |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/06/28/all-7-harry-potter-books-to-film |website=IGN |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107155702/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/06/28/all-7-harry-potter-books-to-film |archive-date=2016-01-07 |access-date=2020-04-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |date=2000-06-20 |title=Euro-AICN Special Report: Harry Potter, and a Little Bit on Aardman's next |work=Ain't it Cool News |url=http://legacy.aintitcool.com/node/6270 |url-status=live |access-date=2007-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417022015/http://legacy.aintitcool.com/node/6270 |archive-date=2020-04-17}}</ref>。[[阿尼克城堡|阿尼克城堡]]和[[格洛斯特座堂|格洛斯特座堂]]最终选为霍格沃兹学院的主要取景地<ref name="JensenEW2001p5">{{Cite news |last1=Jensen |first1=Jeff |last2=Fierman |first2=Daniel |date=2001-09-14 |title=Inside Harry Potter |page=5 |work=Entertainment Weekly |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,254808_5,00.html |url-status=dead |access-date=2010-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101127025007/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,254808_5,00.html |archive-date=2010-11-27}}</ref>，部分场景则在[[哈罗公学|哈罗公学]]取景<ref>{{Cite web |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2000-09-05 |title=Another Hogwarts Location for Potter |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/09/05/another-hogwarts-location-for-potter |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607175330/https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/09/05/another-hogwarts-location-for-potter |archive-date=2019-06-07 |access-date=2020-04-16 |website=IGN}}</ref>。其他戏份在[[达勒姆座堂|达勒姆座堂]]拍摄，为期两周<ref name="LinderIGNSep2000-2">{{Cite web |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2000-09-26 |title=Potter Privet Drive Pics |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/09/26/potter-privet-drive-pics |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170331014421/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/09/26/potter-privet-drive-pics |archive-date=2017-03-31 |access-date=2020-04-16 |website=IGN}}</ref>，包括走廊及部分教室的场景<ref>{{Cite web |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2000-10-03 |title=Potter Pics: Part Two – The Hogwarts Set at Durham Cathedral |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/10/03/potter-pics-part-two-a-the-hogwarts-set-at-durham-cathedral |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170123162943/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/10/03/potter-pics-part-two-a-the-hogwarts-set-at-durham-cathedral |archive-date=2017-01-23 |access-date=2020-04-16 |website=IGN}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Divinity School, Oxford|牛津大学神学院}}成为霍格华兹的医院部（Hospital Wing），[[博德利圖書館|博德利圖書館]]的汉弗莱公爵藏书馆成为霍格华兹的图书馆<ref>{{Cite web |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2000-10-25 |title=Hogwarts Oxford Location Pics & Rowling Speaks |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/10/25/hogwarts-oxford-location-pics-rowling-speaks |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222222455/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/10/25/hogwarts-oxford-location-pics-rowling-speaks |archive-date=2016-12-22 |access-date=2020-04-16 |website=IGN}}</ref>。水蜡树街（Privet Drive）在[[伯克郡|伯克郡]][[布拉克內爾|布拉克內爾]]哨岗回环（Picket Post Close）取景<ref name="LinderIGNSep2000-2" />，这里的拍摄比原计划多个一天，附近居民受到的报酬相应增加<ref name="LinderIGNSep2000-2" />，使得后续作品中的水蜡树街利用在利维斯登工作室搭建好的布景拍摄，成本被证明比实地拍摄要低<ref>{{Cite AV media |title=Harry Potter: Behind the Magic |date=2007-07-07 |last=Shephard, Ben |publisher=ITV1 |medium=TV}}</ref>。位于伦敦的{{tsl|en|High Commission of Australia, London|澳大利亚驻英国公署|澳大利亚驻英国公署大楼}}获选为[[哈利·波特中的地点|古灵阁巫师银行]]的取景地<ref name="JensenEW2001p5" />，[[牛津大学基督堂学院|牛津大学基督堂学院]]获选为霍格华兹的奖杯室<ref name="LinderIGNNov2000">{{Cite web |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2000-11-15 |title=Potter Set News & Pics |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/11/15/potter-set-news-pics |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107155702/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/11/15/potter-set-news-pics |archive-date=2016-01-07 |access-date=2020-04-16 |website=IGN}}</ref>。[[伦敦动物园|伦敦动物园]]是哈利不小心在达力身上放蛇一幕的取景地<ref>{{Cite web |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2001-02-21 |title=Lumos! |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2001/02/21/lumos |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170530210215/http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/02/21/lumos |archive-date=2017-05-30 |access-date=2020-04-16 |website=IGN}}</ref>。取景工作于2001年3月23日结束，收尾工作在2001年7月完成<ref name="SchmitzYahoo">{{Cite web |last=Schmitz |first=Greg Dean |title=Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone (2001) |url=https://movies.yahoo.com/movie/preview/1808404331 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071215132239/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/preview/1808404331 |archive-date=2007-12-15 |access-date=2008-08-09 |website=Yahoo! Movies}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Harry Potter at Leavesden |url=http://www.wbstudiotour.co.uk/en/about-us/harry-potter-at-leavesden |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120923223732/http://www.wbstudiotour.co.uk/en/about-us/harry-potter-at-leavesden |archive-date=2012-09-23 |access-date=2012-09-16 |website=Warner Bros. Studio Tour London – The Making of Harry Potter |quote=Filming began on Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone at Leavesden Studios on Friday 29th September 2000.}}</ref><ref name="TCMNotes" />。

[[File:london-building-leaky-cauldron-2007-07-16.jpg|thumb]]
由于影片在美国上映时的片名与英国不同，所有提到“贤者之石”（Philosopher's Stone）的戏份要拍两遍，一遍是演员说“贤者”（Philosopher's），一遍是说“魔法师”（Sorcerer's）<ref name="SchmitzYahoo" />。小演员们每天拍完四个小时的戏，又要用三个小时完成家庭作用。他们对化妆师制作的假伤口起了兴趣。拉德克利夫被绿色美瞳深深刺激到，因为按照原本的计划，他要戴绿色的美瞳，遮盖自己眼睛原本的蓝色。后来咨询过罗琳的意见，剧组一致同意哈利也可以有蓝眼睛<ref name="ConversationJK&Radcliffe">{{Cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=da6vcVuaqN8 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218150403/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=da6vcVuaqN8 |archive-date=2020-12-18 |url-status=no |title=A Conversation between JK Rowling and Daniel Radcliffe |publisher=Warner Bros. Pictures |year=2011 |place=''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows – Part 2'' |access-date=2020-04-16 |via=YouTube }} {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=da6vcVuaqN8 |date=20201218150403 }}{{cbignore}}</ref>。

=== 設計與視覺效果 ===
{{tsl|en|Judianna Makovsky|朱迪安娜·马可夫斯基}}担任服装设计。至于魁地奇的长袍，她原本考虑原著美国版封面的设计，但后来觉得“混乱”，选择重新设计，为魁地奇穿上了“预科生毛衣、19世纪的击剑马裤和护臂”。布景设计{{tsl|en|Stuart Craig|斯图尔特·克雷格}}在利维斯登工作室搭建场景，包括根据英式大教堂设计的霍格华兹学院大厅。克雷格原计划用现存的古街道拍摄[[对角巷|对角巷]]的戏份，后来改为自行搭景，融合了[[都铎时代建筑|都铎时代]]、[[喬治時代建築|乔治时代]]及{{tsl|en|Queen Anne Style architecture|安妮女皇风格建筑|安妮女皇风格}}元素<ref>{{Cite magazine |last=Cagle |first=Jess |date=2001-11-05 |title=Cinema: The First Look at Harry |url=http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1961973_1961978,00.html |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923041434/http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1961973_1961978,00.html |archive-date=2015-09-23 |access-date=2020-04-16 |magazine=Time}}</ref>。

哥伦布一开始想结合机械木偶及CGI动画打造三頭犬等魔法生物<ref name="LinderIGNMar2000" />。参与制作《[[星際大戰首部曲：威脅潛伏|星際大戰首部曲：威脅潛伏]]》的尼克·杜德曼（Nick Dudman）负责制作所需的假肢，{{tsl|en|Jim Henson's Creature Shop|吉姆·汉森生物店}}提供生物特效<ref>{{Cite web |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2001-01-08 |title=Davis Confirms Potter Role |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2001/01/08/davis-confirms-potter-role |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919104941/http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/01/08/davis-confirms-potter-role |archive-date=2016-09-19 |access-date=2020-04-16 |website=IGN}}</ref>。特效师约翰·科平格（John Coppinger）表示所需的魔法生物需要多番设计<ref>{{Cite web |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2001-01-11 |title=Potter Creature Feature |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2001/01/11/potter-creature-feature |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220011630/http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/01/11/potter-creature-feature |archive-date=2016-12-20 |access-date=2020-04-17 |website=IGN}}</ref>。全片采用近600个特效镜头，多家特效工作联合制作，其中[[光影魔幻工业|光影魔幻工业]]打造奇洛身后的[[伏地魔|伏地魔]]脸庞，[[节奏特效工作室|节奏特效工作室]]将海格的龙宝宝[[魯霸·海格|魯霸]]动画化，{{tsl|en|Sony Pictures Imageworks|索尼影业图像}}制作[[魁地奇|魁地奇]]的戏份<ref>{{Cite news |last1=Jensen |first1=Jeff |last2=Fierman |first2=Daniel |date=2001-09-14 |title=Inside Harry Potter |page=6 |work=Entertainment Weekly |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,254808_6,00.html |url-status=dead |access-date=2010-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101127025012/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,254808_6,00.html |archive-date=2010-11-27}}</ref>。

=== 配樂 ===
{{main|哈利波特－神秘的魔法石 (原聲帶)}}
[[約翰·威廉斯|約翰·威廉斯]]担任配乐<ref>{{Cite web |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2000-08-17 |title=Harry Potter Composer Chosen |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2000/08/17/harry-potter-composer-chosen |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107155701/http://www.ign.com/articles/2000/08/17/harry-potter-composer-chosen |archive-date=2016-01-07 |access-date=2020-04-17 |website=IGN}}</ref>。威廉斯在洛杉矶及[[坦格活德|坦格活德]]家中谱曲，于2001年9月到伦敦录制。其中主题音乐定名为《[[嘿美主題|海德薇主题]]》（''Hedwig's Theme''），威廉斯在最终的配乐中保留该曲，觉得“大家应该会喜欢”，结果成为系列标志性的主题音乐<ref name="LinderIGNJul2001">{{Cite web |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2001-05-23 |title=Potter Postlude |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2001/05/23/potter-postlude |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200704232854/https://www.gamespot.com/amp-articles/sorcerers-stone-ships-out/1100-6085531/ |archive-date=2020-07-04 |access-date=2020-04-17 |website=IGN}}</ref>。[[詹姆斯·霍纳|詹姆斯·霍纳]]是首选的作曲人，但他推掉了邀約<ref>{{Cite web |last=Vishnevetsky |first=Ignatiy |date=2015-06-23 |title=R.I.P. James Horner |url=https://www.avclub.com/r-i-p-james-horner-1798281000 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210607065811/https://www.avclub.com/r-i-p-james-horner-1798281000 |archive-date=2021-06-07 |access-date=2021-06-07 |website=The A.V. Club}}</ref>。原声带专辑于2001年10月30日以CD格式发行<ref name="LinderIGNJul2001" />。

== 重映 ==

2020年3月19日，华纳宣布将于中国大陆重映该片的4K修复3D版，但因[[2019冠状病毒病中国大陆疫情|2019冠状病毒病中国大陆疫情]]影响，上映时间仍未具体公布<ref>{{Cite web|title=华纳兄弟电影的微博_微博|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190218005740/https://www.weibo.com/512365917|accessdate=2020-03-19|date=2019-02-18|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>，最终定档同年8月14日上映<ref>{{cite web |title=助力影院复工!多部好莱坞大片定档8月 《绝地战警3》《1917》&"哈利波特"重映 |url=http://news.mtime.com/2020/07/23/1603206.html |website=Mtime时光网 |accessdate=2020-07-23 |date=2020-07-23 |archive-date=2020-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915085950/http://news.mtime.com/2020/07/23/1603206.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 迴響 ==
=== 評價 ===
《哈利波特：神秘的魔法石》收穫了普遍影評人的積極評價。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的200篇專業影評文章，其中162篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為81%，平均得分7.1分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harry_potter_and_the_sorcerers_stone/ |title=Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone (Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone) (2001) |accessdate=2007-07-08 |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203134925/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harry_potter_and_the_sorcerers_stone/ |archive-date=2013-12-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而基於另一影評網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的37篇評論文章，其中25篇予以好評，0篇差評，12篇褒貶不一，平均分為65（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/video/titles/harrypotterandthesorcerersstone |title=Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone |accessdate=2007-07-20 |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090711202402/http://www.metacritic.com/video/titles/harrypotterandthesorcerersstone |archive-date=2009-07-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影評人[[羅傑·伊伯特|羅傑·伊伯特]]稱《-{zh-hant:神祕的魔法石;zh-cn:哈利·波特与魔法石;}-》是「經典」，給與電影四顆星的滿分，並特別讚揚[[魁地奇|魁地奇]]場景的視覺效果<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20011116/REVIEWS/111160301/1023 |title=Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone |accessdate=2007-07-08 |date=2001-11-16 |first=Roger |last=Ebert |work=[[芝加哥太陽報|Chicago Sun Times]] |authorlink=Roger Ebert |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070709060147/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20011116%2FREVIEWS%2F111160301%2F1023 |archive-date=2007-07-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》雜誌的托德·麥卡錫將電影與《[[亂世佳人|亂世佳人]]》進行了積極的比較，表示：「劇本十分忠實原著，演員選擇是正確的，而演出者的服裝、化妝和效果的匹配，有時超越任何人所想像。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117916310.html |title=Also Playing: Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone|date=2001-11-11|last=McCarthy|first=Todd|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=2010-10-19}}</ref>

=== 票房 ===
這部電影在2001年11月4日於[[倫敦|倫敦]]的[[萊斯特廣場|萊斯特廣場]]舉行世界首演，電影院還特地將場景布置成[[霍格華茲魔法與巫術學院|霍格華茲]]的樣子<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/film/1634408.stm |title=Potter Casts Spell at World Premiere |accessdate=2007-09-23 |date=2001-11-15 |publisher=BBC News Online |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070312191433/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/film/1634408.stm |archive-date=2007-03-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《哈利波特：神秘的魔法石》在票房上極為成功，在美國，首映當天共收穫3230萬美元，打破了先前由《[[星際大戰首部曲：威脅潛伏|星際大戰首部曲：威脅潛伏]]》所保持的單日紀錄。發行的隔天，電影的收入增加到3350萬美元，打破了最大單日的紀錄。總結來說，《-{zh-hant:神祕的魔法石;zh-cn:哈利·波特与魔法石;}-》在第一個週末的票房總額為9030萬美元，超越《[[侏儸紀公園：失落的世界|侏儸紀公園：失落的世界]]》的最高首映週末票房的紀錄<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywood.com/news/Box_Office_Analysis_Harry_Potter_breaks_records/1097810 |title="Harry Potter" Magically Shatters Records |accessdate=2007-09-21 |date=2001-11-18 |publisher=Hollywood.com |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120530043317/http://www.hollywood.com/news/Box_Office_Analysis_Harry_Potter_breaks_records/1097810 |archive-date=2012-05-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，該紀錄保持到隔年5月，才被《[[蜘蛛人_(電影)|蜘蛛人]]》所打破<ref>{{cite news |author=Gray, Brandon |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=1157&p=.htm |title='Spider-Man' Takes Box Office on the Ultimate Spin: $114.8 Million |accessdate=2010-02-07 |date=2002-05-06 |publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130524112812/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=1157&p=.htm |archive-date=2013-05-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影蟬聯了三週的票房冠軍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2001&wknd=47&p=.htm |title=November 23-25, 2001 Weekend 3-day Thanksgiving Weekend |accessdate=2013-11-24 |publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110043504/http://boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2001&wknd=47&p=.htm |archive-date=2013-11-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?view=&yr=2001&wknd=48&p=.htm |title=November 30-December 2, 2001 Weekend |accessdate=2013-11-24 |publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202225515/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?view=&yr=2001&wknd=48&p=.htm |archive-date=2013-12-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。除了以上幾項紀錄，《-{zh-hant:神祕的魔法石;zh-cn:哈利·波特与魔法石;}-》還創下了最高的5天（週三至週日）[[感恩節|感恩節]]週末的票房紀錄，共獲得824萬美元，並維持了12年，直到《[[飢餓遊戲：星火燎原_(電影)|飢餓遊戲：星火燎原]]》的1.11億美元和《[[冰雪奇缘|冰雪奇緣]]》的9400萬美元才被超越<ref>{{cite news|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3758&p=.htm|title=Weekend Report: 'Catching Fire,' 'Frozen' Set Thanksgiving Records|publisher=boxofficemojo.com|accessdate=2013-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202235906/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3758&p=.htm|archive-date=2013-12-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

最終，《-{zh-hant:神祕的魔法石;zh-cn:哈利·波特与魔法石;}-》在全球的票房收入為9.748億美元，美國共收穫3.176億美元，其他地區則為6.57億美元<ref name="BOM">{{cite web |title=Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone (2001) |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=harrypotter.htm |publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |accessdate=2007-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090211185646/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=harrypotter.htm |archive-date=2009-02-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這在當時為歷史上的票房第二高<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/tv_film/newsid_1828000/1828977.stm |title=Potter Makes Movie Chart History |accessdate=2007-07-11 |date=2002-02-19 |work=[[Newsround|Newsround]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090808213415/http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/tv_film/newsid_1828000/1828977.stm |archive-date=2009-08-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，且是該年度票房最高的電影<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2001&p=.htm |title=2001 Worldwide Grosses |accessdate=2007-05-29 |publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070410133146/http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2001&p=.htm |archive-date=2007-04-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截止至2015年，《-{zh-hant:神祕的魔法石;zh-cn:哈利·波特与魔法石;}-》是未考慮通貨膨脹的歷史票房第二十六名，和盈利第二高的哈利波特電影<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/ |title=Worldwide Grosses |accessdate=2010-05-19 |publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100102025933/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/ |archive-date=2010-01-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，僅次於《[[哈利波特：死神的聖物Ⅱ|哈利波特：死神的聖物Ⅱ]]》的13億美元<ref>[http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=harrypotter72.htm Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows Part 2 (2011)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=harrypotter72.htm |date=20170626031016 }}. [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]. Retrieved 31 July 2011.</ref>。根據[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]估計，電影在美國共售出了超過5590萬張門票<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=2016-05-31|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=harrypotter.htm&adjust_yr=1&p=.htm|title=Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone (2001)|publisher=Box Office Mojo|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160804215928/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=harrypotter.htm&adjust_yr=1&p=.htm|archive-date=2016-08-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

