=== 榮譽 ===
電影獲得了3項奧斯卡的提名：[[奧斯卡最佳藝術指導獎|最佳藝術執導]]、[[奥斯卡金像奖最佳服装设计奖|最佳服裝設計]]以及[[約翰·威廉斯_(作曲家)|約翰·威廉斯]]的[[奧斯卡最佳原創音樂獎|最佳原創音樂獎]]<ref name="oscars">{{cite web|url=http://awardsdatabase.oscars.org/ampas_awards/BasicSearch?action=searchLink&displayType=3&BSFilmID=38592|title=Results Page for Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone  – Academy Awards Database|publisher=[[AMPAS|AMPAS]]|accessdate=2010-07-17|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20140609212629/http://awardsdatabase.oscars.org/ampas_awards/BasicSearch?action=searchLink&displayType=3&BSFilmID=38592|archivedate=2014-06-09}}</ref>。《哈利波特：神秘的魔法石》還被提名了[[英国电影学院奖|英國電影學院獎]]的7個獎項，包括[[英国电影学院奖最佳英国电影|最佳英國電影]]、[[羅比·科特瑞恩|羅比·科特瑞恩]]的[[英國電影學院獎最佳男配角|最佳男配角]]，以及{{link-en|英國電影學院獎最佳服裝設計獎|BAFTA Award for Best Costume Design|服裝設計}}、{{link-en|英國電影學院獎生產設計獎|BAFTA Award for Best Production Design|生產設計}}、{{link-en|英國電影學院獎最佳化妝和髮型獎|Doug Sweetland|化妝和髮型}}、{{link-en|英國電影學院獎最佳視覺特效獎|BAFTA Award for Best Special Visual Effects|最佳視覺特效}}與{{link-en|英國電影學院獎最佳音樂獎|BAFTA Award for Best Sound|最佳音樂獎}}<ref name="bafta">{{cite web|url=http://www.bafta.org/awards/film/nominations/?year=2001|title=BAFTA Film Nominations 2001|publisher=[[British_Academy_of_Film_and_Television_Arts|British Academy of Film and Television Arts]]|accessdate=2010-10-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100921081906/http://www.bafta.org/awards/film/nominations/?year=2001|archivedate=2010-09-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該部電影贏得了[[土星獎|土星獎]]的{{link-en|土星獎最佳服裝獎|Saturn Award for Best Costume|最佳服裝獎}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.saturnawards.org/past.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906130320/http://www.saturnawards.org/past.html|title=Past Saturn Awards|publisher=Academy of Science Fiction, Fantasy & Horror Films|accessdate=2010-10-21|archivedate=2014-09-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，並被提名了其他8個獎項<ref name="saturn">{{cite web|url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/NEFxGLGKxjVvJN|title=The 2001 Saturn Awards|publisher=MovieWeb|date=2002-06-13|accessdate=2010-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090820005111/http://www.movieweb.com/news/NEFxGLGKxjVvJN|archive-date=2009-08-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影還獲得了美國演員工會和服裝設計師工會的其他獎項<ref name="artios">{{cite web|url=http://www.castingsociety.com/component/content/article/42-artios-awards/80-previous-artios-award-winners/#2001|title=Artios Award Winners|publisher=Casting Society of America|accessdate=2010-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120822021527/http://www.castingsociety.com/component/content/article/42-artios-awards/80-previous-artios-award-winners#2001|archive-date=2012-08-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="cdg">{{cite web |url=http://www.costumedesignersguild.com/aw-archive/awarch.asp?archid=2002 |title=WINNERS FOR THE 4th ANNUAL COSTUME DESIGNERS GUILD AWARDS |publisher=Costume Designers Guild |accessdate=2010-10-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708194732/http://www.costumedesignersguild.com/aw-archive/awarch.asp?archid=2002 |archivedate=2011-07-08 }}</ref>。《-{zh-hant:神祕的魔法石;zh-cn:哈利·波特与魔法石;}-》被提名美國電影學會獎的特殊效果獎，且獲得了廣播影評人獎的最佳現場動作家庭電影，提名包含最佳兒童表演（[[丹尼爾·雷德克里夫|丹尼爾·雷德克里夫]]）和最佳作曲家（約翰·威廉斯）<ref name="bfca">{{cite web |url=http://www.bfca.org/ccawards/2001.php |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65SuyBcDE?url=http://www.bfca.org/ccawards/2001.php |title=2001 Broadcast Film Critics Choice Award Winners and Nominations |publisher=Broadcast Film Critics Association |accessdate=2010-10-19 |archivedate=2012-02-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2005年，《-{zh-hant:神祕的魔法石;zh-cn:哈利·波特与魔法石;}-》被提名至由[[美國電影學會|美國電影學會]]評選的[[AFI百年電影史電影配樂|AFI百年電影史電影配樂]]中，但未能入選<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.afi.com/Docs/100Years/scores250.pdf |title=AFI's 100 Years of Film Scores Nominees |format=PDF |date= |accessdate=2016-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106023410/http://www.afi.com/Docs/100years/scores250.pdf |archive-date=2013-11-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

